"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T03:50:44.000Z","msg":"境外有樓同境外有樓收租係兩回事黎<br />\n<br />\n到政府講到香港永久居民喺外蒙古有間祖屋都要賣咗佢先可以申請公屋時<br />\n你班友又嘈政府call錢托市推高樓價etc...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再者如果咁執行法其實想玩鳩人好簡單<br />\n去北非用人地個名買間負值樓再舉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人外地有樓唔代表佢喺香港冇實際居住需要<br />\n始終佢係香港永久居民，而外地有樓又唔代表佢入到境同住到<br />\n直布羅陀都打擊唔到西班牙有樓申請公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最多劃大D條界<br />\n你限大灣區有樓就唔可以申請公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁四川、湖南堆假結婚雞又可以繼續鄉下收租<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要限就要限成個中國<br />\n咁呢個我支持嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後會有好多80/90後公屋居民去台灣/越南買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b4515a1135189f1784e290e4d9f811a92579cd","tid":973203,"uid":46737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:16:14.000Z","msg":"一律取消所有特快審批，查完先放樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4223bd6323175f37c63a34500455924898275d1c","tid":973203,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:17:05.000Z","msg":"港獨派:泛民鳩做again, 香港獨立咪解決到"},{"pid":"042d28633f5168d6fa6f164a8ffc5bac109ff0d8","tid":973203,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:20:44.000Z","msg":"打擊香港人濫用公屋<br />\n<br />\n歡迎支那狗種申請"},{"pid":"8d8a330687fc13aa4358a98b19a4f93dff547815","tid":973203,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:02:53.000Z","msg":"淋病唔會接受。"},{"pid":"67e8c08d822cdfc0b2804ebbecc4bb5dccbd71c8","tid":973203,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae08e7c430c0500805a52d52b70226dbee996820","tid":973203,"uid":48769,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T03:15:43.000Z","msg":"如果靠篤灰有獎金<br />\n呢